<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Contact - Instasnapper</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen animate-gradient bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 via-purple-500 to-pink-500 text-white">
  
  <!-- Header -->
  <header class="flex items-center justify-between sm:justify-center px-4 sm:px-8 py-4 border-b border-black/10 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-md shadow-md">
    <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
      <img src="../assets/images/logo.gif" alt="Logo" class="h-10 w-10 sm:h-12 sm:w-12" />
      <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-[500] bg-gradient-to-r from-[#db00ff] to-[#22c8fe] text-transparent bg-clip-text">InstaSnapper</h1>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Contact Section -->
  <div class="flex flex-col justify-center py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-20 text-left">
    <div class="text-white space-y-5 text-base sm:text-lg max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
      
      <p>📬 Got a question, suggestion, or feedback? We're always happy to hear from you. Whether you have a feature request or need help using InstaSnapper, feel free to reach out!</p>
      
      <!-- <p>🧑‍💻 <strong>Website Owner:</strong> Sumit Dhir</p> -->
      
      <p>📧 <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:sumitdhir171@gmail.com" class="text-blue-400 underline">sumitdhir171@gmail.com</a></p>
      
      <p>🕐 We aim to respond within 24-48 hours. Your queries are important to us, and we make sure to give you the best support possible.</p>
      
      <p>📍 Please note that InstaSnapper is an independent tool, and we are not affiliated with Instagram, YouTube, or any other platform. For platform-specific issues, kindly contact them directly.</p>
      
      <p>💡 For collaborations, feature ideas, or any kind of creative partnership, drop us an email. Let’s make downloading content more efficient — together!</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="bg-gray-100 py-8 text-center text-gray-700">
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center items-center sm:space-x-8 space-y-2 sm:space-y-0 text-[18px] font-medium mb-4">
      <a href="/about" class="hover:text-purple-600 transition">About</a>
      <a href="/privacy" class="hover:text-purple-600 transition">Policy</a>
      <a href="/contact" class="hover:text-purple-600 transition">Contact</a>
    </div>
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-[500] bg-gradient-to-r from-[#db00ff] to-[#22c8fe] text-transparent bg-clip-text">
      InstaSnapper
    </h1>
  </footer>

  <!-- Animation -->
  <style>
    @keyframes gradient {
      0% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
      50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
      100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
    }
    .animate-gradient {
      background-size: 200% 200%;
      animation: gradient 6s ease infinite;
    }
  </style>
</body>
</html>
